            <pb n="1"/>

            <p>Congregation Bnai Jeshurun <placeName>New York</placeName></p>
            <p>Rev. Sir</p>

            <p rend="indent(1)">I am instructed by the President<lb/> and Trustees of this Congregation to inform
                you<lb/> that the consecration of their new Synagogue<lb/> Green Street will please
                God take place on<lb/> Thursday next the 25<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Ins<hi rend="sup"
                    >t</hi> on which solemn<lb/> occasion the favour of your presence is
                requested.<lb/>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">The service will commence at 3 ocl. PM.<lb/> The consecration&#8211;discourse will be
                delivered by<lb/> the Rev. <persName>Morris J. Raphall</persName>&#44; M.A. PhD<hi
                    rend="sup">r</hi> Rabbi&#8211;preacher<lb/> to the Congregation. The musical
                arrangements<lb/> under the direction of the Rev. <persName>A. Leo</persName>&#44;
                Hazan<lb/> minister to the Congregation<lb/> I have the honour to be<lb/> Rev.
                Sir<lb/> Very Respectfully (By order<lb/><persName role="author">Henry
                    Goldsmith</persName><lb/> Sec<hi rend="sup">t</hi>.</p>
            <p>14 West Broadway place</p>
            <p>New York 18th. Sept<hi rend="sup">r</hi>. 5611&#47;51.</p>
            <p>Rev. <addressee>I. Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">&#38;. &#38;. &#38;</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>

        </body>
